Crotale saw the missile also diving to take out Pacifix....

Slag blasted some fire at the roaring Tremor but it just flew around 
his hardened steel.  Tremor now just in front of Slugslinger 
transformed, his two guns forming one and landing in his hand, the 
other reaching down to grab Slugslinger.
